entry.title: About Me
entry.content:
A perhaps determined romantic, an optimistic salty fish, and an undefined soul free agent.
Not a muggle, for sure.

entry.title: Hello Strangers
entry.content: Welcome ~ I use this blog to record some interesting things as well as my personal introduction. My idol is Steph Curry of the Warriors. If you are fan of Steph, then we are friends.
